column5: AIMT AIMT short covering has begun Finally Short Interest down over 500000 shares in latest NASDAQ 15 day report This has been partially responsible for the stock leveling out or starting to outperform the XBI If the short covering continues we should have seen the lows or perhaps at least not see a new low in a retest My guess is now if the stk sells off below 20 more short covering will commence It would make sense given where we are relative to the Ad Com
